snippet.title: Pamilya Roces: Amber and Hugo’s affair | Episode 9
snippet.description:
Aired (October 18, 2018): Dagdag gulo na naman ang dala ni Amber ngayong naakit niya ang asawa ni Crystal na si Hugo. 

Watch episodes of ‘Pamilya Roces’ weeknights on GMA Telebabad, starring Carla Abellana, Gabbi Garcia, Sophie Albert, Shaira Diaz, and newest Kapuso actress Jasmine Curtis Smith. Also in the cast are veteran actors Roi Vinzon, Gloria Diaz, Snooky Serna, Ana Roces, Elizabeth Oropesa with Rocco Nacino, Mika Dela Cruz, Andre Paras, Manolo Pedrosa, and Christian Bautista.
